Type: Package
Package: DirectLiNGAM
Title: Direct LiNGAM for Causal Discovery
Version: 0.1.0.9000
Authors@R: person("Osamu", "Morimoto", email = "galactic.supermarket@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: R implementation of Direct LiNGAM algorithm for causal discovery
    based on non-Gaussianity. Supports OLS, LASSO, and Adaptive LASSO
    for adjacency matrix estimation.
    Based on the Python implementation by Ikeuchi et al. (2023)
    <https://github.com/cdt15/lingam>.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
URL: https://github.com/morimotoosamu/DirectLiNGAM
BugReports: https://github.com/morimotoosamu/DirectLiNGAM/issues
Depends: 
    R (>= 3.5)
Imports:
    stats,
    grDevices
Suggests:
    glmnet,
    DiagrammeR,
    ggplot2,
    nortest,
    tseries
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
